1324
01:08:19,634 --> 01:08:21,301
Do you realize that?

1325
01:08:21,435 --> 01:08:25,405
The intimate relationship
between killer and victim.

1326
01:08:26,440 --> 01:08:29,744
I can feel every ripple
coursing through your body.

1327
01:08:29,877 --> 01:08:33,146
