throbbing through this chain.

1328
01:08:33,280 --> 01:08:34,916
You want to know
the best part, Jimmy?

1329
01:08:35,049 --> 01:08:37,986
The best part,
when I look in your eyes...

1330
01:08:38,118 --> 01:08:41,488
