1357
01:10:39,306 --> 01:10:41,743
I want you there, James!

1358
01:10:58,626 --> 01:10:59,861
You gonna stay?

1359
01:11:02,262 --> 01:11:03,497
You sure?

1360
01:11:05,298 --> 01:11:07,201
