1409
01:15:26,627 --> 01:15:28,529
I didn't say that!

1410
01:15:28,662 --> 01:15:30,064
I want it!

1411
01:15:30,197 --> 01:15:31,232
I didn't say that!

1412
01:15:31,365 --> 01:15:33,667
I didn't...

