01:17:23,512 --> 01:17:25,446
And it's signed
by Governor Jennings.

1449
01:17:26,113 --> 01:17:28,315
Does the condemned
wish to review the warrant?

1450
01:17:35,456 --> 01:17:38,225
No. I trust you.

1451
01:17:56,744 --> 01:17:58,279
