1486
01:21:13,073 --> 01:21:14,441
What's your answer, James?

1487
01:21:17,478 --> 01:21:19,647
Do you accept
my master's offer?

1488
01:21:24,952 --> 01:21:28,255
<i>Mene, mene, tekel, upharshin.</i>

1489
01:21:42,871 --> 01:21:44,371
What the hell
