01:21:46,641 --> 01:21:48,976
Bring the generator
to full load.

1492
01:22:14,935 --> 01:22:15,969
Hit him.

1493
01:22:55,476 --> 01:22:56,845
I can still make out activity.

1494
01:22:56,977 --> 01:22:58,312
All right. Stand clear.

1495
01:23:01,716 --> 01:23:02,750
Hit him again.

