1614
01:29:50,324 --> 01:29:51,893
wrote a book, and you're here,

1615
01:29:52,026 --> 01:29:54,996
-and you wanted it published.
-Yes.

1616
01:29:56,264 --> 01:29:57,999
Well, no. I...

1617
